data.description: Step into this pristine 2-story home and be transported to a world of modern convenience and luxury. With its spacious layout, thoughtful amenities, and Wi-Fi CERTIFIED smart features, this a Tavola gem.  On the main level, a gracious living space that flows seamlessly between the living room and dining room. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with all the essentials for creating memorable meals, including 36-inch designer cabinets, granite countertops, a breakfast nook, and a large pantry. Unwind upstairs in the game room, with four bedrooms provide ample space for everyone. The master bedroom is a sanctuary of relaxation, with a master bath featuring a separate tub and shower, and a walk-in closet. Make your appointment today!
